title: Flower Classification
subtitle: 14 Types of Flower Image Classification
description: The dataset contains 14 types of flower images, including 13618 training images and 98 validation images, with a total data size of 202MB, and supports the recognition of the following flower types: carnation, iris, bluebells, golden english, roses, fallen nephews, tulips, marigolds, dandelions, chrysanthemums, black-eyed daisies, water lilies, sunflowers, and daisies.
